{"tid":324081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在香港 你我的家鄉香港","createTime":"2017-07-16T07:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T08:28:32.000Z","uid":37764,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74eb0baddf793d8803ed1307173caf0fb8371652","tid":324081,"uid":37764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jvUYsHMIJC4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjvUYsHMIJC4&d=n5LJYnjb56BN7rXI7crcNP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=8d39e7ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jvUYsHMIJC4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港近年真係不斷每況愈下 <br />\n但當香港人都放棄香港 香港就真係玩完 <br />\n所以希望大家聽完呢首歌會冇咁灰心啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366430deac700b65294b7ba2d991f93a1412c419","tid":324081,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"有次聽到眼濕濕，但諗起唱果個人就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbcc76329c2f14041b723d0f9af5fe9a1d3618d","tid":324081,"uid":37764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:25:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次聽到眼濕濕，但諗起唱果個人就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁首歌係得佢唱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇其他version分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3e279280cadcec20ad32a845d8553c25e376f7","tid":324081,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:29:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dac5ad9f06108bb22dd943f21bb9f02fd91b5f4c","tid":324081,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家乜撚野鄉 又想水班香港人留底俾中共搾壓？<br />\n上幾代人為左逃離中共先走落黎，<br />\n而家中共殺到黎 你條檬撚仲唔走<br />\n你祖先死左都激翻生，生著個後代咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩祖先？你講令到香港腐化嗰班廢物老而不？<br />\n我就真係想激醒佢，得佢睇清楚佢嗰代做港豬做到依家香港點"},{"pid":"53634e3458027f08471bfac7cb3837980d76c0f4","tid":324081,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有次聽到眼濕濕，但諗起唱果個人就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁首歌係得佢唱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇其他version分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唱果個都移撚左民得閒番黎Cap下水就算<br />\n<br />\n個公信力會唔會有D問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c737a53b4d89c2da1e4282cc3048f73436df81e0","tid":324081,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6732ea61fe940db080a1f0f384ac932c483d2ce1","tid":324081,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}